{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777007194584,"sessionID":"ses_24259126dffeTdrtnwWatL0lCR","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_y4Th9zU1u4piGLhQ3tB25M7z","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\server\\deploy\\DEPLOY.md","limit":2000,"offset":1},"output":"<path>D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\server\\deploy\\DEPLOY.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Chat Soft Server 部署说明\n2: \n3: 更新时间：2026-04-19\n4: \n5: 本文档说明服务器上 `Chat Soft` 主服务的实际部署方式。\n6: \n7: 当前推荐方案：\n8: \n9: - 代码目录：`/opt/chat_soft`\n10: - 服务目录：`/opt/chat_soft/server/api`\n11: - 进程管理：`PM2`\n12: - 包管理：`pnpm`\n13: - 默认端口：`3000`\n14: \n15: ## 1. 环境要求\n16: \n17: 服务器需要安装：\n18: \n19: - Node.js 20+\n20: - npm\n21: \n22: 安装 `pnpm`：\n23: \n24: ```bash\n25: npm install -g pnpm@10.18.0\n26: ```\n27: \n28: 安装 `PM2`：\n29: \n30: ```bash\n31: npm install -g pm2\n32: ```\n33: \n34: 如果命令不在 `PATH` 中，直接使用：\n35: \n36: ```bash\n37: /usr/local/bin/pnpm\n38: /usr/local/bin/pm2\n39: ```\n40: \n41: ## 2. 上传项目\n42: \n43: 把整个 `chat_soft` 目录上传到服务器，例如：\n44: \n45: ```bash\n46: scp -r chat_soft root@YOUR_SERVER_IP:/opt/chat_soft\n47: ```\n48: \n49: ## 3. 安装依赖与构建\n50: \n51: ```bash\n52: cd /opt/chat_soft\n53: /usr/local/bin/pnpm install --frozen-lockfile\n54: /usr/local/bin/pnpm --filter @chat-soft/server build\n55: ```\n56: \n57: ## 4. 启动服务\n58: \n59: ```bash\n60: cd /opt/chat_soft\n61: HOST=0.0.0.0 PORT=3000 /usr/local/bin/pm2 start /opt/chat_soft/server/api/dist/index.js --name chat-soft-server\n62: /usr/local/bin/pm2 save\n63: ```\n64: \n65: ## 5. 检查状态\n66: \n67: ```bash\n68: /usr/local/bin/pm2 list\n69: curl http://127.0.0.1:3000/health\n70: ```\n71: \n72: 预期返回：\n73: \n74: ```json\n75: {\"ok\":true}\n76: ```\n77: \n78: 注意：\n79: \n80: - 根路径 `/` 没有定义路由\n81: - 访问 `http://SERVER_IP:3000/` 返回 `404` 是正常的\n82: - 请用 `/health` 验证服务是否可用\n83: \n84: ## 6. 更新服务\n85: \n86: ```bash\n87: cd /opt/chat_soft\n88: git pull\n89: /usr/local/bin/pnpm install --frozen-lockfile\n90: /usr/local/bin/pnpm --filter @chat-soft/server build\n91: /usr/local/bin/pm2 restart chat-soft-server\n92: ```\n93: \n94: ## 7. 查看日志\n95: \n96: ```bash\n97: /usr/local/bin/pm2 logs chat-soft-server\n98: ```\n99: \n100: ## 8. 需要开放的端口\n101: \n102: - `3000`\n103: \n104: ## 9. 第一版连接方式\n105: \n106: - HTTP API：`http://SERVER_IP:3000`\n107: - 健康检查：`http://SERVER_IP:3000/health`\n108: - WebSocket：`ws://SERVER_IP:3000/ws`\n\n(End of file - total 108 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Chat Soft Server 部署说明\n\n更新时间：2026-04-19\n\n本文档说明服务器上 `Chat Soft` 主服务的实际部署方式。\n\n当前推荐方案：\n\n- 代码目录：`/opt/chat_soft`\n- 服务目录：`/opt/chat_soft/server/api`\n- 进程管理：`PM2`\n- 包管理：`pnpm`\n- 默认端口：`3000`\n\n## 1. 环境要求\n\n服务器需要安装：\n\n- Node.js 20+\n- npm","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\server\\deploy\\DEPLOY.md","time":{"start":1777007194525,"end":1777007194583}},"id":"prt_dbde1f194001gcTcvSkdeKdKz5","sessionID":"ses_24259126dffeTdrtnwWatL0lCR","messageID":"msg_dbde1ce99001bq1AB2uX8CaZev"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777007194601,"sessionID":"ses_24259126dffeTdrtnwWatL0lCR","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_1WwDmfQbsSrevkXynzDMaT0k","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\docs\\operations_runbook.md","limit":2000,"offset":1},"output":"<path>D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\docs\\operations_runbook.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Chat Soft 运行与运维手册\n2: \n3: 更新时间：2026-04-17\n4: \n5: 本文档用于统一记录 `Chat Soft` 各模块的：\n6: \n7: - 更新方式\n8: - 重启方式\n9: - 启动方式\n10: - 验证方式\n11: - 任务进度查看方式\n12: - 常见排错方式\n13: \n14: 适用对象：\n15: \n16: - 远端服务器上的 `chat-soft` 主服务\n17: - 本机 `Codex Mirror`\n18: - 本机 `Codex VS Code Bridge`\n19: - 本机桌面端\n20: - 本机移动端\n21: \n22: ---\n23: \n24: ## 1. 目录与组件\n25: \n26: 项目根目录：\n27: \n28: - `D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft`\n29: \n30: 服务器部署目录：\n31: \n32: - `/opt/chat_soft`\n33: \n34: 主要组件：\n35: \n36: - 主服务：`@chat-soft/server`\n37: - 桌面端：`@chat-soft/desktop`\n38: - 移动端：`@chat-soft/mobile`\n39: - Codex 镜像服务：`@chat-soft/codex-mirror-server`\n40: - Codex 镜像调试页：`@chat-soft/codex-mirror-debug`\n41: - VS Code 插件桥接：`tools/codex-vscode-bridge`\n42: \n43: ---\n44: \n45: ## 2. 服务器主服务\n46: \n47: 当前线上服务器的实际运行方式：\n48: \n49: - 项目目录：`/opt/chat_soft`\n50: - 服务目录：`/opt/chat_soft/server/api`\n51: - 进程管理：`PM2`\n52: - 服务名：`chat-soft-server`\n53: - 端口：`3000`\n54: - 健康检查：`/health`\n55: \n56: 注意：\n57: \n58: - 这个服务没有定义根路由 `/`\n59: - 访问 `http://SERVER_IP:3000/` 返回 `404` 是正常现象\n60: - 正确验证地址是 `http://SERVER_IP:3000/health`\n61: \n62: ### 2.1 首次部署或补装环境\n63: \n64: 服务器需要：\n65: \n66: - Node.js 20+\n67: - npm\n68: - PM2\n69: \n70: 如果 `pnpm` 不在 `PATH` 中，统一使用绝对路径：\n71: \n72: ```bash\n73: /usr/local/bin/pnpm\n74: ```\n75: \n76: 如果 `pm2` 不在 `PATH` 中，统一使用绝对路径：\n77: \n78: ```bash\n79: /usr/local/bin/pm2\n80: ```\n81: \n82: 安装 `pnpm`：\n83: \n84: ```bash\n85: npm install -g pnpm@10.18.0\n86: ```\n87: \n88: 安装 `PM2`：\n89: \n90: ```bash\n91: npm install -g pm2\n92: ```\n93: \n94: ### 2.2 首次启动\n95: \n96: 在服务器执行：\n97: \n98: ```bash\n99: cd /opt/chat_soft\n100: /usr/local/bin/pnpm install --frozen-lockfile\n101: /usr/local/bin/pnpm --filter @chat-soft/server build\n102: HOST=0.0.0.0 PORT=3000 /usr/local/bin/pm2 start /opt/chat_soft/server/api/dist/index.js --name chat-soft-server\n103: /usr/local/bin/pm2 save\n104: ```\n105: \n106: ### 2.3 日常更新\n107: \n108: 在服务器执行：\n109: \n110: ```bash\n111: cd /opt/chat_soft\n112: git pull\n113: /usr/local/bin/pnpm install --frozen-lockfile\n114: /usr/local/bin/pnpm --filter @chat-soft/server build\n115: /usr/local/bin/pm2 restart chat-soft-server\n116: ```\n117: \n118: 如果不是 `git pull` 方式更新，而是直接覆盖项目目录，也同样执行后 3 条命令即可。\n119: \n120: ### 2.4 启动与重启\n121: \n122: 启动服务：\n123: \n124: ```bash\n125: /usr/local/bin/pm2 start /opt/chat_soft/server/api/dist/index.js --name chat-soft-server\n126: ```\n127: \n128: 重启服务：\n129: \n130: ```bash\n131: /usr/local/bin/pm2 restart chat-soft-server\n132: ```\n133: \n134: 停止服务：\n135: \n136: ```bash\n137: /usr/local/bin/pm2 stop chat-soft-server\n138: ```\n139: \n140: 删除服务：\n141: \n142: ```bash\n143: /usr/local/bin/pm2 delete chat-soft-server\n144: ```\n145: \n146: 查看状态：\n147: \n148: ```bash\n149: /usr/local/bin/pm2 list\n150: ```\n151: \n152: ### 2.5 服务器验证\n153: \n154: 本机回环验证：\n155: \n156: ```bash\n157: curl http://127.0.0.1:3000/health\n158: curl http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/agents\n159: curl http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/conversations\n160: ```\n161: \n162: 公网验证：\n163: \n164: ```bash\n165: curl http://SERVER_IP:3000/health\n166: ```\n167: \n168: 正常时应看到：\n169: \n170: - `/health` 返回 `{\"ok\":true}`\n171: - `/api/agents` 返回 agent 列表\n172: - `/api/conversations` 返回会话列表\n173: \n174: ### 2.6 服务器日志\n175: \n176: 查看服务日志：\n177: \n178: ```bash\n179: /usr/local/bin/pm2 logs chat-soft-server\n180: ```\n181: \n182: 查看最近状态：\n183: \n184: ```bash\n185: /usr/local/bin/pm2 list\n186: ```\n187: \n188: 如果只想确认端口是否被监听：\n189: \n190: ```bash\n191: ss -ltnp | grep :3000\n192: ```\n193: \n194: ### 2.7 常见问题\n195: \n196: 访问 `/` 返回 `404`：\n197: \n198: - 正常现象\n199: - 这个项目没有首页路由\n200: - 用 `/health` 检查是否存活\n201: \n202: `listen EADDRINUSE: address already in use 0.0.0.0:3000`：\n203: \n204: - 说明 `3000` 端口已经被现有服务占用\n205: - 不要手工重复执行 `pnpm --filter @chat-soft/server start`\n206: - 先看：\n207: \n208: ```bash\n209: ss -ltnp | grep :3000\n210: /usr/local/bin/pm2 list\n211: ```\n212: \n213: 如果确认是旧服务异常占用，再执行：\n214: \n215: ```bash\n216: /usr/local/bin/pm2 restart chat-soft-server\n217: ```\n218: \n219: `pnpm: command not found`：\n220: \n221: - 直接使用：\n222: \n223: ```bash\n224: /usr/local/bin/pnpm\n225: ```\n226: \n227: `pm2: command not found`：\n228: \n229: - 直接使用：\n230: \n231: ```bash\n232: /usr/local/bin/pm2\n233: ```\n234: \n235: 本机 `curl http://127.0.0.1:3000/health` 正常，但公网访问失败：\n236: \n237: - 先确认服务已监听 `0.0.0.0:3000`\n238: - 再检查云服务器安全组是否放行 `3000`\n239: - 再检查系统防火墙是否放行 `3000`\n240: \n241: ### 2.8 维护时的最短操作路径\n242: \n243: 只更新代码并重启：\n244: \n245: ```bash\n246: cd /opt/chat_soft\n247: git pull\n248: /usr/local/bin/pnpm install --frozen-lockfile\n249: /usr/local/bin/pnpm --filter @chat-soft/server build\n250: /usr/local/bin/pm2 restart chat-soft-server\n251: ```\n252: \n253: 只检查是否还活着：\n254: \n255: ```bash\n256: curl http://127.0.0.1:3000/health\n257: ```\n258: \n259: 只看服务日志：\n260: \n261: ```bash\n262: /usr/local/bin/pm2 logs chat-soft-server\n263: ```\n264: \n265: ---\n266: \n267: ## 3. Codex 镜像服务\n268: \n269: 说明：\n270: \n271: - 这是本机运行的本地服务\n272: - 默认端口：`3090`\n273: - 当前启动命令应使用新的构建入口，不能再用旧的 `dist/index.js`\n274: \n275: ### 3.1 本机更新\n276: \n277: 在本机项目目录执行：\n278: \n279: ```powershell\n280: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\n281: git pull\n282: pnpm install\n283: pnpm --filter @chat-soft/codex-mirror-server build\n284: pnpm --filter @chat-soft/codex-mirror-debug build\n285: ```\n286: \n287: ### 3.2 本机启动\n288: \n289: 开发模式：\n290: \n291: ```powershell\n292: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\n293: pnpm dev:codex-mirror-server\n294: ```\n295: \n296: 生产构建启动：\n297: \n298: ```powershell\n299: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\server\\codex-mirror\n300: node dist/server/codex-mirror/src/index.js\n301: ```\n302: \n303: ### 3.3 本机重启\n304: \n305: 如果是前台终端运行：\n306: \n307: - 先 `Ctrl+C`\n308: - 再重新执行启动命令\n309: \n310: 如果是后台 `Start-Process` 跑的：\n311: \n312: 先杀掉监听 `3090` 端口的进程：\n313: \n314: ```powershell\n315: Get-NetTCPConnection -LocalPort 3090 -State Listen | Select-Object -ExpandProperty OwningProcess\n316: Stop-Process -Id <PID> -Force\n317: ```\n318: \n319: 然后重新启动：\n320: \n321: ```powershell\n322: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\server\\codex-mirror\n323: node dist/server/codex-mirror/src/index.js\n324: ```\n325: \n326: ### 3.4 本机验证\n327: \n328: 建议统一使用：\n329: \n330: ```powershell\n331: curl.exe --noproxy \"*\" http://127.0.0.1:3090/health\n332: curl.exe --noproxy \"*\" http://127.0.0.1:3090/api/codex-mirror/status\n333: curl.exe --noproxy \"*\" http://127.0.0.1:3090/api/codex-mirror/models\n334: curl.exe --noproxy \"*\" http://127.0.0.1:3090/api/codex-mirror/sessions\n335: ```\n336: \n337: 说明：\n338: \n339: - 当前机器上 `Invoke-RestMethod` 可能因为代理链路异常返回 `502`\n340: - 本地联调优先用 `curl.exe --noproxy \"*\"`\n341: \n342: ### 3.5 发送测试消息\n343: \n344: 先创建会话：\n345: \n346: ```powershell\n347: curl.exe --noproxy \"*\" -X POST \"http://127.0.0.1:3090/api/codex-mirror/sessions\" -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" --data-binary \"{\\\"modelId\\\":\\\"gpt-5.4\\\"}\"\n348: ```\n349: \n350: 再向某个会话发消息：\n351: \n352: ```powershell\n353: curl.exe --noproxy \"*\" -X POST \"http://127.0.0.1:3090/api/codex-mirror/sessions/<SESSION_ID>/messages\" -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" --data-binary \"{\\\"text\\\":\\\"请只回复四个汉字\\\",\\\"waitForConfirmation\\\":true}\"\n354: ```\n355: \n356: 查看消息：\n357: \n358: ```powershell\n359: curl.exe --noproxy \"*\" \"http://127.0.0.1:3090/api/codex-mirror/sessions/<SESSION_ID>/messages\"\n360: ```\n361: \n362: ### 3.6 调试页启动\n363: \n364: ```powershell\n365: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\n366: pnpm dev:codex-mirror-debug\n367: ```\n368: \n369: 构建：\n370: \n371: ```powershell\n372: pnpm --filter @chat-soft/codex-mirror-debug build\n373: ```\n374: \n375: ---\n376: \n377: ## 4. VS Code Codex Bridge\n378: \n379: 目录：\n380: \n381: - `D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\tools\\codex-vscode-bridge`\n382: \n383: ### 4.1 更新\n384: \n385: ```powershell\n386: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\tools\\codex-vscode-bridge\n387: npm install\n388: npm run build\n389: ```\n390: \n391: ### 4.2 启动方式\n392: \n393: 这个模块不是独立 exe，而是 VS Code 扩展。\n394: \n395: 使用方式：\n396: \n397: 1. 在 VS Code 打开该目录\n398: 2. 确保扩展已安装/加载\n399: 3. 执行 `Developer: Reload Window`\n400: \n401: ### 4.3 常用命令\n402: \n403: 在 VS Code 命令面板中可用：\n404: \n405: - `Chat Soft Codex: Start Bridge`\n406: - `Chat Soft Codex: Stop Bridge`\n407: - `Chat Soft Codex: Show Available Models`\n408: - `Chat Soft Codex: Reset Conversation History`\n409: - `Chat Soft Codex: Bind Current Thread`\n410: \n411: ### 4.4 验证\n412: \n413: 验证思路：\n414: \n415: - VS Code 里能看到扩展已启用\n416: - 输出面板里能看到 `Chat Soft Codex Bridge`\n417: - 手机端/服务端能看到 `Codex Agent`\n418: - 发送消息后 bridge 有日志\n419: \n420: ### 4.5 日志\n421: \n422: 看 VS Code 输出面板：\n423: \n424: - `View`\n425: - `Output`\n426: - 右上角通道选择 `Chat Soft Codex Bridge`\n427: \n428: ---\n429: \n430: ## 5. 桌面端\n431: \n432: ### 5.1 更新与构建\n433: \n434: ```powershell\n435: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\n436: pnpm install\n437: pnpm --filter @chat-soft/desktop build\n438: ```\n439: \n440: ### 5.2 开发启动\n441: \n442: ```powershell\n443: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\n444: pnpm dev:desktop\n445: ```\n446: \n447: ### 5.3 本地 agent 启动\n448: \n449: ```powershell\n450: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\n451: pnpm --filter @chat-soft/desktop agent:start\n452: ```\n453: \n454: 说明：\n455: \n456: - 这个命令会启动本地 agent 网关\n457: - 默认连本机 `http://127.0.0.1:3000`\n458: - 如果要连云服务器，启动前先设置环境变量 `CHAT_SOFT_SERVER_BASE_URL`\n459: - 启动后会自动向服务器注册至少两个 agent：\n460:   - `llm-chat`\n461:   - `opencode`\n462: - `opencode` agent 会调用本机安装好的 `opencodecli` 或 `opencode` CLI\n463: - 手机端拉取到最新会话列表后，可以像和普通好友聊天一样直接给 `代码开发助手` 发送文本消息\n464: - `opencode` agent 现已支持在聊天中直接用指令管理 session 和模型\n465: \n466: 如果本机没有把 CLI 加进环境变量，`opencode` agent 会在会话里回复启动失败原因。\n467: \n468: 连接云服务器示例：\n469: \n470: ```powershell\n471: $env:CHAT_SOFT_SERVER_BASE_URL = \"http://39.106.125.149:3000\"\n472: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\n473: pnpm --filter @chat-soft/desktop agent:start\n474: ```\n475: \n476: 如果要让 `opencode` 以自动批准模式执行本地读写和命令操作，可以再加：\n477: \n478: ```powershell\n479: $env:CHAT_SOFT_SERVER_BASE_URL = \"http://39.106.125.149:3000\"\n480: $env:CHAT_SOFT_OPENCODE_AUTO_APPROVE = \"true\"\n481: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\n482: pnpm --filter @chat-soft/desktop agent:start\n483: ```\n484: \n485: 说明：\n486: \n487: - 这会给 `opencode run` 自动附加 `--dangerously-skip-permissions`\n488: - 适合你希望手机端体验尽量接近本地终端直连时使用\n489: - 风险也更高，手机里发出的文件操作、命令执行、目录创建会直接落地到本机\n490: \n491: 如果你不想每次手动设置环境变量，可以直接双击运行：\n492: \n493: ```text\n494: D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\start_opencode_agent.cmd\n495: ```\n496: \n497: `opencode` 会话内可用指令：\n498: \n499: ```text\n500: /help\n501: /providers\n502: /models\n503: /model provider/model\n504: /session\n505: /session current\n506: /session use <SESSION_ID>\n507: /session reset\n508: ```\n509: \n510: 说明：\n511: \n512: - `/providers` 查看当前本机已配置的 provider\n513: - `/models` 查看可用模型\n514: - `/model provider/model` 切换后续消息使用的模型\n515: - `/session` 查看可切换的历史 session\n516: - `/session use <SESSION_ID>` 绑定到指定 session，继续那条会话\n517: - `/session reset` 清空当前绑定，下一条普通消息会新建 session\n518: \n519: ### 5.4 验证\n520: \n521: 重点看：\n522: \n523: - 桌面窗口是否正常打开\n524: - 是否能拉到会话列表\n525: - 是否能正常发送文本消息\n526: - agent 是否在线\n527: - 手机上的会话列表里是否出现 `代码开发助手`\n528: - 给 `代码开发助手` 发一条文本后是否收到 CLI 返回结果\n529: \n530: ---\n531: \n532: ## 6. 移动端\n533: \n534: ### 6.1 前端更新\n535: \n536: ```powershell\n537: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\n538: pnpm install\n539: pnpm --filter @chat-soft/mobile build\n540: pnpm --filter @chat-soft/mobile cap:sync\n541: ```\n542: \n543: ### 6.2 开发预览\n544: \n545: ```powershell\n546: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\n547: pnpm dev:mobile\n548: ```\n549: \n550: ### 6.3 Android 构建同步\n551: \n552: ```powershell\n553: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\n554: pnpm --filter @chat-soft/mobile cap:sync\n555: ```\n556: \n557: 如果要从 Android Studio 构建：\n558: \n559: - 打开 `apps/mobile/android`\n560: - 重新同步 Gradle\n561: - 构建并安装\n562: \n563: ### 6.4 USB 安装常用命令\n564: \n565: 确认设备：\n566: \n567: ```powershell\n568: adb devices\n569: ```\n570: \n571: 安装 APK：\n572: \n573: ```powershell\n574: adb install -r <APK_PATH>\n575: ```\n576: \n577: 彻底重装：\n578: \n579: ```powershell\n580: adb uninstall <包名>\n581: adb install <APK_PATH>\n582: ```\n583: \n584: ### 6.5 移动端验证\n585: \n586: 重点看：\n587: \n588: - 应用是否能正常打开\n589: - 是否能拉到会话列表\n590: - 文本发送接收是否正常\n591: - agent 会话是否可见\n592: - 媒体消息是否能显示正确类型\n593: \n594: ---\n595: \n596: ## 7. 一键常用流程\n597: \n598: ### 7.1 服务器更新 + 重启 + 验证\n599: \n600: ```bash\n601: cd /opt/chat_soft\n602: git pull\n603: /usr/local/bin/pnpm install\n604: /usr/local/bin/pnpm --filter @chat-soft/server build\n605: systemctl restart chat-soft\n606: systemctl status chat-soft --no-pager\n607: curl http://127.0.0.1:3000/health\n608: curl http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/agents\n609: curl http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/conversations\n610: ```\n611: \n612: ### 7.2 本机 Codex 镜像更新 + 重启 + 验证\n613: \n614: ```powershell\n615: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\n616: pnpm install\n617: pnpm --filter @chat-soft/codex-mirror-server build\n618: Get-NetTCPConnection -LocalPort 3090 -State Listen | Select-Object -ExpandProperty OwningProcess\n619: Stop-Process -Id <PID> -Force\n620: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\server\\codex-mirror\n621: node dist/server/codex-mirror/src/index.js\n622: ```\n623: \n624: 新开一个终端验证：\n625: \n626: ```powershell\n627: curl.exe --noproxy \"*\" http://127.0.0.1:3090/health\n628: curl.exe --noproxy \"*\" http://127.0.0.1:3090/api/codex-mirror/status\n629: curl.exe --noproxy \"*\" http://127.0.0.1:3090/api/codex-mirror/sessions\n630: ```\n631: \n632: ### 7.3 VS Code Bridge 更新 + 重新加载\n633: \n634: ```powershell\n635: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\tools\\codex-vscode-bridge\n636: npm install\n637: npm run build\n638: ```\n639: \n640: 然后在 VS Code 执行：\n641: \n642: - `Developer: Reload Window`\n643: \n644: ---\n645: \n646: ## 8. 任务进度怎么看\n647: \n648: ### 8.1 看本地代码状态\n649: \n650: ```powershell\n651: git -C D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft status --short\n652: git -C D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft log --oneline -n 10\n653: ```\n654: \n655: ### 8.2 看某个模块是否已经构建\n656: \n657: 主服务：\n658: \n659: ```powershell\n660: Test-Path D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\server\\api\\dist\\index.js\n661: ```\n662: \n663: Codex 镜像：\n664: \n665: ```powershell\n666: Test-Path D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\server\\codex-mirror\\dist\\server\\codex-mirror\\src\\index.js\n667: ```\n668: \n669: 桥接扩展：\n670: \n671: ```powershell\n672: Test-Path D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\tools\\codex-vscode-bridge\\dist\\extension.js\n673: ```\n674: \n675: ### 8.3 看服务是否在线\n676: \n677: 服务器主服务：\n678: \n679: ```bash\n680: systemctl status chat-soft --no-pager\n681: ```\n682: \n683: 本机 Codex 镜像：\n684: \n685: ```powershell\n686: Get-NetTCPConnection -LocalPort 3090 -State Listen\n687: ```\n688: \n689: ### 8.4 看当前文档与方案进度\n690: \n691: 重点文档：\n692: \n693: - [operations_runbook.md](D:/agent_workspace/projects/chat_soft/docs/operations_runbook.md)\n694: - [codex_mirror_requirements_and_architecture.md](D:/agent_workspace/projects/chat_soft/docs/codex_mirror_requirements_and_architecture.md)\n695: - [codex_mirror_technical_validation.md](D:/agent_workspace/projects/chat_soft/docs/codex_mirror_technical_validation.md)\n696: \n697: ---\n698: \n699: ## 9. 常见排错顺序\n700: \n701: 如果你不知道先查哪里，就按这个顺序：\n702: \n703: 1. 先确认进程/端口是否真的起来了\n704: 2. 再打 `/health`\n705: 3. 再看日志\n706: 4. 再看是不是旧构建产物/旧入口\n707: 5. 再看是不是代理问题\n708: \n709: 本机联调常见坑：\n710: \n711: - PowerShell 自带请求工具走错代理\n712: - 杀掉的是旧进程，但新进程没真正拉起\n713: - 启动命令仍然指向旧的构建入口\n714: \n715: 服务器常见坑：\n716: \n717: - `pnpm` 路径不对\n718: - 重启后立刻 `curl`，服务还没完全起来\n719: - `git pull` 拉到的是新代码，但没重新 build\n720: \n721: ---\n722: \n723: ## 10. 当前建议\n724: \n725: 日常最稳的工作习惯：\n726: \n727: - 服务器用绝对路径 `/usr/local/bin/pnpm`\n728: - 本机接口验证统一用 `curl.exe --noproxy \"*\"`\n729: - Codex 镜像启动统一用：\n730: \n731: ```powershell\n732: node D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\server\\codex-mirror\\dist\\server\\codex-mirror\\src\\index.js\n733: ```\n734: \n735: - 每次改完 bridge 记得：\n736:   - `npm run build`\n737:   - VS Code `Reload Window`\n\n(End of file - total 737 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Chat Soft 运行与运维手册\n\n更新时间：2026-04-17\n\n本文档用于统一记录 `Chat Soft` 各模块的：\n\n- 更新方式\n- 重启方式\n- 启动方式\n- 验证方式\n- 任务进度查看方式\n- 常见排错方式\n\n适用对象：\n\n- 远端服务器上的 `chat-soft` 主服务\n- 本机 `Codex Mirror`\n- 本机 `Codex VS Code Bridge`\n- 本机桌面端\n- 本机移动端","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\docs\\operations_runbook.md","time":{"start":1777007194503,"end":1777007194600}},"id":"prt_dbde1f176001tJNDA3CizQNnGv","sessionID":"ses_24259126dffeTdrtnwWatL0lCR","messageID":"msg_dbde1ce99001bq1AB2uX8CaZev"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777007194623,"sessionID":"ses_24259126dffeTdrtnwWatL0lCR","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_O6HX6Ga3We0I0vY4YLqDGgxa","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\docs\\server_maintenance.md","limit":2000,"offset":1},"output":"<path>D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\docs\\server_maintenance.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Chat Soft 服务器维护手册\n2: \n3: 更新时间：2026-04-19\n4: \n5: 本文档只覆盖服务器上的 `Chat Soft` 主服务维护。\n6: \n7: 适用范围：\n8: \n9: - 服务器项目目录：`/opt/chat_soft`\n10: - 服务目录：`/opt/chat_soft/server/api`\n11: - 进程管理：`PM2`\n12: - 服务名：`chat-soft-server`\n13: - 默认端口：`3000`\n14: \n15: ## 1. 当前部署事实\n16: \n17: 当前服务器不是用 `systemd` 托管，也不是依赖 Docker 常驻运行。\n18: \n19: 当前实际运行方式：\n20: \n21: - 使用 `PM2` 托管 Node 进程\n22: - 实际启动文件：`/opt/chat_soft/server/api/dist/index.js`\n23: - 对外监听：`0.0.0.0:3000`\n24: - 健康检查：`/health`\n25: \n26: 注意：\n27: \n28: - 访问 `http://SERVER_IP:3000/` 返回 `404` 是正常现象\n29: - 根路径 `/` 没有定义路由\n30: - 正确检查地址是 `http://SERVER_IP:3000/health`\n31: \n32: ## 2. 环境要求\n33: \n34: 服务器需要安装：\n35: \n36: - Node.js 20+\n37: - npm\n38: - pnpm 10.18.0\n39: - PM2\n40: \n41: 如果命令不在 `PATH` 中，统一使用绝对路径：\n42: \n43: ```bash\n44: /usr/local/bin/pnpm\n45: /usr/local/bin/pm2\n46: ```\n47: \n48: ## 3. 首次部署\n49: \n50: ### 3.1 安装工具\n51: \n52: ```bash\n53: npm install -g pnpm@10.18.0\n54: npm install -g pm2\n55: ```\n56: \n57: ### 3.2 安装依赖并构建\n58: \n59: ```bash\n60: cd /opt/chat_soft\n61: /usr/local/bin/pnpm install --frozen-lockfile\n62: /usr/local/bin/pnpm --filter @chat-soft/server build\n63: ```\n64: \n65: ### 3.3 用 PM2 启动\n66: \n67: ```bash\n68: cd /opt/chat_soft\n69: HOST=0.0.0.0 PORT=3000 /usr/local/bin/pm2 start /opt/chat_soft/server/api/dist/index.js --name chat-soft-server\n70: /usr/local/bin/pm2 save\n71: ```\n72: \n73: ### 3.4 启动后验证\n74: \n75: ```bash\n76: curl http://127.0.0.1:3000/health\n77: ```\n78: \n79: 预期返回：\n80: \n81: ```json\n82: {\"ok\":true}\n83: ```\n84: \n85: ## 4. 日常更新\n86: \n87: 代码更新后，在服务器执行：\n88: \n89: ```bash\n90: cd /opt/chat_soft\n91: git pull\n92: /usr/local/bin/pnpm install --frozen-lockfile\n93: /usr/local/bin/pnpm --filter @chat-soft/server build\n94: /usr/local/bin/pm2 restart chat-soft-server\n95: ```\n96: \n97: 如果不是 `git pull`，而是直接覆盖项目目录，也照样执行后 3 条命令。\n98: \n99: ## 5. 常用运维命令\n100: \n101: 查看状态：\n102: \n103: ```bash\n104: /usr/local/bin/pm2 list\n105: ```\n106: \n107: 查看日志：\n108: \n109: ```bash\n110: /usr/local/bin/pm2 logs chat-soft-server\n111: ```\n112: \n113: 重启服务：\n114: \n115: ```bash\n116: /usr/local/bin/pm2 restart chat-soft-server\n117: ```\n118: \n119: 停止服务：\n120: \n121: ```bash\n122: /usr/local/bin/pm2 stop chat-soft-server\n123: ```\n124: \n125: 删除服务：\n126: \n127: ```bash\n128: /usr/local/bin/pm2 delete chat-soft-server\n129: ```\n130: \n131: 重新创建服务：\n132: \n133: ```bash\n134: cd /opt/chat_soft\n135: HOST=0.0.0.0 PORT=3000 /usr/local/bin/pm2 start /opt/chat_soft/server/api/dist/index.js --name chat-soft-server\n136: /usr/local/bin/pm2 save\n137: ```\n138: \n139: 确认端口监听：\n140: \n141: ```bash\n142: ss -ltnp | grep :3000\n143: ```\n144: \n145: ## 6. 服务验证\n146: \n147: 本机验证：\n148: \n149: ```bash\n150: curl http://127.0.0.1:3000/health\n151: curl http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/agents\n152: curl http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/conversations\n153: ```\n154: \n155: 公网验证：\n156: \n157: ```bash\n158: curl http://SERVER_IP:3000/health\n159: ```\n160: \n161: 正常结果：\n162: \n163: - `/health` 返回 `{\"ok\":true}`\n164: - `/api/agents` 返回 JSON\n165: - `/api/conversations` 返回 JSON\n166: \n167: ## 7. 常见故障\n168: \n169: ### 7.1 访问 `/` 返回 404\n170: \n171: 这是正常现象。\n172: \n173: 原因：\n174: \n175: - 服务没有定义首页路由 `/`\n176: - 不能用首页判断服务是否启动\n177: \n178: 正确检查方式：\n179: \n180: ```bash\n181: curl http://127.0.0.1:3000/health\n182: ```\n183: \n184: ### 7.2 `listen EADDRINUSE: address already in use 0.0.0.0:3000`\n185: \n186: 说明 `3000` 已经被已有进程占用，常见原因是 `PM2` 已经在托管服务。\n187: \n188: 先检查：\n189: \n190: ```bash\n191: ss -ltnp | grep :3000\n192: /usr/local/bin/pm2 list\n193: ```\n194: \n195: 如果服务本来就在运行，不要重复执行前台 `start` 命令。\n196: \n197: 正确做法：\n198: \n199: ```bash\n200: /usr/local/bin/pm2 restart chat-soft-server\n201: ```\n202: \n203: ### 7.3 `pnpm: command not found`\n204: \n205: 改用绝对路径：\n206: \n207: ```bash\n208: /usr/local/bin/pnpm\n209: ```\n210: \n211: 如果还没安装：\n212: \n213: ```bash\n214: npm install -g pnpm@10.18.0\n215: ```\n216: \n217: ### 7.4 `pm2: command not found`\n218: \n219: 改用绝对路径：\n220: \n221: ```bash\n222: /usr/local/bin/pm2\n223: ```\n224: \n225: 如果还没安装：\n226: \n227: ```bash\n228: npm install -g pm2\n229: ```\n230: \n231: ### 7.5 本机可访问，公网不可访问\n232: \n233: 如果本机执行：\n234: \n235: ```bash\n236: curl http://127.0.0.1:3000/health\n237: ```\n238: \n239: 返回正常，但公网打不开，通常是以下原因：\n240: \n241: - 云服务器安全组未放行 `3000`\n242: - 系统防火墙未放行 `3000`\n243: - 反向代理未配置\n244: \n245: 先确认监听：\n246: \n247: ```bash\n248: ss -ltnp | grep :3000\n249: ```\n250: \n251: ## 8. 推荐的最短维护流程\n252: \n253: 更新并重启：\n254: \n255: ```bash\n256: cd /opt/chat_soft\n257: git pull\n258: /usr/local/bin/pnpm install --frozen-lockfile\n259: /usr/local/bin/pnpm --filter @chat-soft/server build\n260: /usr/local/bin/pm2 restart chat-soft-server\n261: ```\n262: \n263: 只查看运行状态：\n264: \n265: ```bash\n266: /usr/local/bin/pm2 list\n267: curl http://127.0.0.1:3000/health\n268: ```\n269: \n270: 只查看日志：\n271: \n272: ```bash\n273: /usr/local/bin/pm2 logs chat-soft-server\n274: ```\n\n(End of file - total 274 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Chat Soft 服务器维护手册\n\n更新时间：2026-04-19\n\n本文档只覆盖服务器上的 `Chat Soft` 主服务维护。\n\n适用范围：\n\n- 服务器项目目录：`/opt/chat_soft`\n- 服务目录：`/opt/chat_soft/server/api`\n- 进程管理：`PM2`\n- 服务名：`chat-soft-server`\n- 默认端口：`3000`\n\n## 1. 当前部署事实\n\n当前服务器不是用 `systemd` 托管，也不是依赖 Docker 常驻运行。\n\n当前实际运行方式：\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\docs\\server_maintenance.md","time":{"start":1777007194515,"end":1777007194619}},"id":"prt_dbde1f189001LiFy6HY13K8edY","sessionID":"ses_24259126dffeTdrtnwWatL0lCR","messageID":"msg_dbde1ce99001bq1AB2uX8CaZev"}}
