{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777007245714,"sessionID":"ses_24259126dffeTdrtnwWatL0lCR","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_5PRb5rQHkoXwTHEitUmcXCFA","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\docs\\operations_runbook.md","limit":140,"offset":584},"output":"<path>D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\docs\\operations_runbook.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n584: ### 6.5 移动端验证\n585: \n586: 重点看：\n587: \n588: - 应用是否能正常打开\n589: - 是否能拉到会话列表\n590: - 文本发送接收是否正常\n591: - agent 会话是否可见\n592: - 媒体消息是否能显示正确类型\n593: \n594: ### 6.6 网页端公网部署记录（2026-04-24）\n595: \n596: 当前已把 `@chat-soft/mobile` 作为网页端部署到阿里云服务器，可用手机浏览器访问：\n597: \n598: ```text\n599: http://39.106.125.149/\n600: ```\n601: \n602: 当前实际运行方式：\n603: \n604: - 前端构建产物目录：`/www/wwwroot/chat-soft`\n605: - 静态网页进程管理：`PM2`\n606: - 静态网页服务名：`chat-soft-web`\n607: - 静态网页端口：`80`\n608: - 后端 API 地址：`http://39.106.125.149:3000`\n609: - 后端服务名：`chat-soft-server`\n610: \n611: 本次更新内容：\n612: \n613: - 给网页端增加前端访问门禁：\n614:   - 用户名：`chisado`\n615:   - 密码：`chisado233`\n616:   - 登录状态保存在浏览器 `localStorage`。\n617:   - 这是轻量前端门禁，不等同于后端鉴权；如需更强安全，应改为后端鉴权或 Nginx/BT Basic Auth。\n618: - 修复单会话/默认会话场景下输入发送不可用：\n619:   - 新增有效会话兜底逻辑，会优先使用当前会话，其次使用第一个会话，最后兜底到 `primary`。\n620: - 修复手机网页会话页底部输入栏不可见：\n621:   - 聊天页使用 `100dvh` 高度并禁止整页溢出。\n622:   - 消息列表区域单独滚动。\n623:   - 底部 composer 固定参与布局并提高层级，避免被消息列表挤出屏幕。\n624: \n625: 本地构建命令：\n626: \n627: ```powershell\n628: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\n629: pnpm --filter @chat-soft/mobile build\n630: ```\n631: \n632: 当前手动同步部署流程：\n633: \n634: ```powershell\n635: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\n636: pnpm --filter @chat-soft/mobile build\n637: \n638: # 上传 apps/mobile/dist 到服务器临时目录 /tmp/chat-soft-dist-upload\n639: # 然后在服务器执行：\n640: ```\n641: \n642: ```bash\n643: set -e\n644: ts=$(date +%Y%m%d%H%M%S)\n645: mkdir -p /www/wwwroot/chat-soft\n646: if [ -n \"$(ls -A /www/wwwroot/chat-soft 2>/dev/null)\" ]; then\n647:   tar -C /www/wwwroot -czf /www/wwwroot/chat-soft.backup.$ts.tar.gz chat-soft\n648: fi\n649: rm -rf /www/wwwroot/chat-soft/*\n650: cp -a /tmp/chat-soft-dist-upload/. /www/wwwroot/chat-soft/\n651: /usr/local/bin/pm2 restart chat-soft-web --update-env\n652: ```\n653: \n654: 验证命令：\n655: \n656: ```powershell\n657: Invoke-WebRequest -UseBasicParsing -Uri \"http://39.106.125.149/\" -TimeoutSec 10\n658: Invoke-WebRequest -UseBasicParsing -Uri \"http://39.106.125.149:3000/health\" -TimeoutSec 10\n659: ```\n660: \n661: 预期：\n662: \n663: - 网页返回 `200`。\n664: - 后端健康检查返回 `{\"ok\":true}`。\n665: - 手机打开网页后先显示登录页，登录后进入会话列表。\n666: - 进入会话后底部能看到 `+ / 输入消息 发送` 输入栏。\n667: \n668: ---\n669: \n670: ## 7. 一键常用流程\n671: \n672: ### 7.1 服务器更新 + 重启 + 验证\n673: \n674: ```bash\n675: cd /opt/chat_soft\n676: git pull\n677: /usr/local/bin/pnpm install\n678: /usr/local/bin/pnpm --filter @chat-soft/server build\n679: systemctl restart chat-soft\n680: systemctl status chat-soft --no-pager\n681: curl http://127.0.0.1:3000/health\n682: curl http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/agents\n683: curl http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/conversations\n684: ```\n685: \n686: ### 7.2 本机 Codex 镜像更新 + 重启 + 验证\n687: \n688: ```powershell\n689: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\n690: pnpm install\n691: pnpm --filter @chat-soft/codex-mirror-server build\n692: Get-NetTCPConnection -LocalPort 3090 -State Listen | Select-Object -ExpandProperty OwningProcess\n693: Stop-Process -Id <PID> -Force\n694: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\server\\codex-mirror\n695: node dist/server/codex-mirror/src/index.js\n696: ```\n697: \n698: 新开一个终端验证：\n699: \n700: ```powershell\n701: curl.exe --noproxy \"*\" http://127.0.0.1:3090/health\n702: curl.exe --noproxy \"*\" http://127.0.0.1:3090/api/codex-mirror/status\n703: curl.exe --noproxy \"*\" http://127.0.0.1:3090/api/codex-mirror/sessions\n704: ```\n705: \n706: ### 7.3 VS Code Bridge 更新 + 重新加载\n707: \n708: ```powershell\n709: cd D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\tools\\codex-vscode-bridge\n710: npm install\n711: npm run build\n712: ```\n713: \n714: 然后在 VS Code 执行：\n715: \n716: - `Developer: Reload Window`\n717: \n718: ---\n719: \n720: ## 8. 任务进度怎么看\n721: \n722: ### 8.1 看本地代码状态\n723: \n\n(Showing lines 584-723 of 811. Use offset=724 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"### 6.5 移动端验证\n\n重点看：\n\n- 应用是否能正常打开\n- 是否能拉到会话列表\n- 文本发送接收是否正常\n- agent 会话是否可见\n- 媒体消息是否能显示正确类型\n\n### 6.6 网页端公网部署记录（2026-04-24）\n\n当前已把 `@chat-soft/mobile` 作为网页端部署到阿里云服务器，可用手机浏览器访问：\n\n```text\nhttp://39.106.125.149/\n```\n\n当前实际运行方式：\n","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"agent_workspace\\projects\\chat_soft\\docs\\operations_runbook.md","time":{"start":1777007245663,"end":1777007245711}},"id":"prt_dbde2b434001aJfEa1AxJAi1CJ","sessionID":"ses_24259126dffeTdrtnwWatL0lCR","messageID":"msg_dbde28bb9001aXsc4Iw9RjZ4Om"}}
